include ./includes/mixins

// CONTAINER FOR EMAIL
table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="table-layout: fixed;")
  tr
    td(align="center" bgcolor=aztecGold)

      // EMAIL START
      // wrapper
      table(class="wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600")
        tr
          td
            include ./includes/top-matter
            include ./includes/header

        include ./includes/banner

        tr
          td
            //- Add border to this table when we need it
            table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="table-layout: fixed;")
              tr
                td(class="padding-extra25-top" align="center" bgcolor=aztecGold style="padding: 25px 0px 15px 0px;")
                  // wrapper 
                  table(class="wrapper" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="600")
                    tr
                      td
                        table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" align="center" class="wrapper")

                          tr
                            td(align="center" class="padding-no-bottom" style="padding: 10px 0px 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #{lighterGray};")
                              table(border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="480" align="center" class="wrapper")
                                +kicker('LIMITED-TIME OFFER', textColor)

                                //- HEADLINE
                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text-headline" style="padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-family: #{ffMedium}; font-weight: 600; font-size: 42px; text-align: center; line-height: 50px; color: #{red};") Celebrate 125 years of osteopathic medicine and save $125 off OMED
                                +subhead('Don’t delay, our FINAL flash sale ends on Sept. 6.', textColor)

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};") 
                                    | This is a milestone you don’t want to miss! Join thousands of your DO colleagues at #[+grafLink('OMED', omedUrl, red)], Oct. 7-10 in Philadelphia, to celebrate 125 years of osteopathic heritage. #[span(style="#{grafStyleEmph}").body-text Use code ANNIVERSARY to save $125] off OMED registration.

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};") 

                                    | This year’s conference will feature unique historical exhibits and immersive experiences, including a special anniversary exhibit curated by A.T. Still University and the Museum of Osteopathic Medicine. Through the power of 3-D imagery, OMED attendees will be transported back in time to the birth of osteopathic medicine in Kirksville, Missouri. It’s an OMED journey like no other you’ve experienced!

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};") 
                                    | In addition to celebrating the profession’s history, don’t miss out on countless opportunities for education and networking, including peer-to-peer learning meet-ups in our new Braindates Lounge. Get inspired at conference-wide General Sessions, TED-style talks and panel discussions focused on advancing your career and improving patient care. #[+grafLink('Experience everything', 'http://mydigitalpublication.com/publication/?i=403769#{"issue_id":403769,"page":0}', red)] OMED has to offer. You belong. Here.

                                tr
                                  td(class="body-text" style="font-family: #{ffBook}; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; padding: 0px 0px 25px; font-weight: normal; text-align: left; color: #{textColor};") 

                                    | Use code #[span(style="#{grafStyleEmph}").body-text ANNIVERSARY] to save $125 off the current full registration rate. Can’t stay for the whole conference? Take advantage of our low one-day rate.


                                //tr
                                  //td(class="body-text" style=grafStyleEmphWhite) 

                                +cta('Register Today', housingUrl, red)

                                //tr
                                  //td(class="body-text" style=grafStyleEmphWhite) 

                                +disclaimer('Promotion is for member or nonmember DOs and codes cannot be combined with other promotions or applied to one-day rate.')
                                +disclaimer('Photos courtesy of the Museum of Osteopathic Medicine, Kirksville, Missouri')
        include ./includes/footer
